46
00:04:39,530 --> 00:04:40,530
[Kriminal]: Itigil mo na!

47
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,110
[Lom]: Ibaba mo ang baril!

48
00:04:43,210 --> 00:04:44,850
[Lom]: Itigil mo na!

49
